OL,5, A court in Argentina has sentenced a   
OL,6, former policeman who worked at one of  
OL,7, the most notorious torture centres     
OL,8, during the country's military rule to  
OL,9, 15 years in prison.                    
OL,11,FMario Sandoval, 69, was found guilty of
OL,12,Fabducting and torturing left-wing      
OL,13,Fstudent Hernan Abriata, who disappeared
OL,14,Fin 1976 and is presumed dead.          
OL,16,FSandoval fled Argentina after the end  
OL,17,Fof military rule and settled in France,
OL,18,Fwhere he became a university lecturer. 
OL,20,FHe was extradited in 2019.             
